obo:ECO_0006042  a  owl:Class .

gomodel:SYNGO_5396  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1: S1PR2 was detected in synaptosomal biochemical fractions prepared from mouse cortex, with slight enrichment in the synaptosome-subfraction enriches the active zone (membrane) as compared to synaptosomes. S1PR2 was also detected in the postsynaptic fraction, albeit at slightly lower level than synaptosomes (and much lower than active zone fraction).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Synaptosomal fractionation was modified from Morato et al. [37]. Briefly, the mouse cortex was homogenized in 1 mL of isolation buffer ...\"\n\nantibody:\nRabbit anti-S1PR2, 1:500 (WB)/1:250 (IFn)/1:100 (IFs), Origene (AP01311PU-N)" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
